Date: Tue, 3 Mar 2026 21:19:30 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: replace sequential checkout with atomic PostgreSQL RPC
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add checkout_and_place_order() PG stored procedure (see 01_atomic_checkout.sql)
  - Validates all cart items with row-level locks (prevents overselling)
  - Creates order + order_items + decrements inventory in one transaction
  - Auto-rollback on any failure — no more partial orders
  - Structured error codes: CART_EMPTY, INSUFFICIENT_STOCK, PRODUCT_UNAVAILABLE
- Rewrite src/lib/api.ts checkout() to call single supabase.rpc() instead of
  7 sequential client-side DB calls
- Remove dead edge function helpers (createProduct, updateProduct, etc.)
---
 src/lib/api.ts | 177 +++++++++----------------------------------------
 1 file changed, 32 insertions(+), 145 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/lib/api.ts b/src/lib/api.ts
